    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Naval bases that build, repair, dock, or convert warships, and are manned by civilian engineers and workers and administered by engineer duty officers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
